      "span_text": "A primary tool in the study of the representation theory of Mp(W ) has been the theta correspondence, utilizing the classical oscillator representation ω ψ . For example, such liftings were recently used by Gan-Ichino to extend the notion of Arthur parameter to Mp(W ) A [CITATION_1]"
